[@Watermelon mosaic virus#Virus*] ([$WMV#Virus*]) is one of the major viruses infecting [$cucurbit crops#Plant*] worldwide.
Although [$WMV#Virus*] is very common worldwide, little is known about the biological traits of [$WMV#Virus*] isolates from China.
